<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/21100>
    dc:description "Figure 10. A Thymalus limbatus B Phloiophilus edwardsi C Eronyxa marginicollis D Decamerus haemorhoidalis E Diontolobus punctatipennis F Afrocyrona ciskeiensis G Afrocyrona dwesae H Grynoma sp., New Zealand I Grynoma diluta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/21100" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/21103>
    dc:description "Map 11. A distribution of the tribe Decamerini including the newly described genus † Cretamerus. A position of Eronyxa is indicated." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/21103" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/21108>
    dc:description "Figure 13. A-B Calitys scabra (A head and pronotum B elytral apex with interlocking mechanism) C-D Acalanthis quadrisignata (C apex of protibia with hooked spur and lateral spines D sculpture of frons with punctures conjoined into wrinkles) E-H Gymnocheilis sp., Cameroon (E head F protibia G elytral apex H detail of scales)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/21108" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

